Spring discussion group backend

This is a discussion group built using
-->spring boot
-->spring boot data jpa
-->spring security
-->mail service
-->thymeleaf
-->jwt
-->jwt encryption
-->mysql
-->lombok
-->mapstruct
-->swagger

After register ,user login to the system and continue to the group

User register is verified through email verification key

For every login it sends a encrypted jwt token

User session is managed by encrypted jwt token

User can create a subject or a group

User can create post ,like ,comment ,upvote ,downvote the post

For every subject or group user can post and others can discuss about this post

